{"tid":1375334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[政務司跪低] 張建宗高度表揚警務人員盡忠職守","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:03:54.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2af5484b5110f3b89f800102c3b8dee16354c7ed","tid":1375334,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日前因向公眾道歉，而引起多個警察協會不滿的政務司司長張建宗發表網誌。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗撰文，記述月中與幾名學生到天文台參觀，令他聯想到天氣縱然陰晴不定，只要沉著應對再大風雨過後總會有晴天。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗周五就警方在元朗襲擊事件中的處理手法向公眾道歉，引起多個警察協會不滿，政務司司長辦公室指，張建宗絕對支持及衷心感謝警隊的執法工作，亦高度表揚警務人員在困難期間承受重大壓力仍然盡忠職守，致力維持社會治安，會盡快安排與相關警務人員協會會面，澄清誤會及加强溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357018&amp;fbclid=IwAR19KEh5ouuqJ4-ABzYiIio0fdrJCzrB2R0jfKa1Tc5fzNB_fdXZyCPwbYc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357018%26fbclid%3DIwAR19KEh5ouuqJ4-ABzYiIio0fdrJCzrB2R0jfKa1Tc5fzNB_fdXZyCPwbYc&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=2b33682b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357018%26fbclid%3DIwAR19KEh5ouuqJ4-ABzYiIio0fdrJCzrB2R0jfKa1Tc5fzNB_fdXZyCPwbYc&h=de17aa9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357018&amp;fbclid=IwAR19KEh5ouuqJ4-ABzYiIio0fdrJCzrB2R0jfKa1Tc5fzNB_fdXZyCPwbYc</a>"},{"pid":"627b1bc9f74daef4bb5deb3a7ce0089786e7514f","tid":1375334,"uid":277666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"邊有老闆同下屬認低威<br />\n<br />\n真係狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"8816861b81d695c49d7a6b1e7e13a61b914990eb","tid":1375334,"uid":180404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"香港已經無救<br />\n<br />\n正式進入軍政府時代"},{"pid":"050ee6d9da39e3355ad5d2ef8d6daa6cd0d61e32","tid":1375334,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8816861b81d695c49d7a6b1e7e13a61b914990eb","tid":1375334,"uid":180404,"like":1,